<div class="container py-4">
  <div class="text-center mb-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-danger">Emergency Medical Info</h1>
    <p class="lead">Japan • 日本</p>
  </div>

  <div class="row g-4 mb-5">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="card border-danger shadow-sm h-100">
        <div class="card-body text-center">
          <h2 class="h1 fw-bold text-danger mb-0">119</h2>
          <p class="fs-4 fw-bold">Ambulance / Fire</p>
          <p class="text-muted small">Kyūkyūsha (救急車) / Kaji (火事)</p>
          <hr>
          <p class="card-text text-start small">
            * Toll-free from any phone.<br>
            * Public phones: Press the <strong>red button</strong> first.<br>
            * Say: <strong>"Kyūkyū desu"</strong> (It is a medical emergency).
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="card border-warning shadow-sm h-100">
        <div class="card-body text-center">
          <h2 class="h1 fw-bold text-dark mb-0">#7119</h2>
          <p class="fs-4 fw-bold">Medical Consultation</p>
          <p class="text-muted small">Non-Emergency Help</p>
          <hr>
          <p class="card-text text-start small">
            * Call if you aren't sure if you need an ambulance.<br>
            * Provides advice on whether to see a doctor or call 119.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="border-bottom pb-2 mb-3">Communication Help (Point to these)</h3>
  <div class="list-group shadow-sm">
    <div class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center py-3">
      <div>
        <p class="mb-0 fw-bold">Please call an ambulance.</p>
        <p class="mb-0 text-muted small">Kyūkyūsha o yonde kudasai.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="fs-5 fw-bold text-primary">救急車を呼んでください</span>
    </div>

    <div class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center py-3">
      <div>
        <p class="mb-0 fw-bold">I need a doctor.</p>
        <p class="mb-0 text-muted small">Isha o yonde kudasai.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="fs-5 fw-bold text-primary">医者を呼んでください</span>
    </div>

    <div class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center py-3">
      <div>
        <p class="mb-0 fw-bold">I am in pain / It hurts here.</p>
        <p class="mb-0 text-muted small">Itai desu.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="fs-5 fw-bold text-primary">痛いです</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-5 p-3 bg-light border rounded">
    <h5><i class="bi bi-info-circle"></i> Items to take to the hospital:</h5>
    <ul class="mb-0">
      <li>Passport / Residence Card (Zairyū Card)</li>
      <li>Health Insurance Card (Hokenshō)</li>
      <li>Cash (Many clinics in Japan do not take cards)</li>
      <li>Current Medications or your "Okusuri Techō" (Medication Notebook)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
